{"metadata":{"symbolKind":"struct","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents14OUDSSwitchItemV","roleHeading":"Structure","modules":[{"name":"OUDSComponents"}],"fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSSwitchItem","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"OUDSSwitchItem","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSSwitchItem","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo"}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","text":"MainActor"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSSwitchItem"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"Layouts","text":"Layouts","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The component can be rendered as two different layouts:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"default","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": the component has a leading indicator, a label and optional helper texts, and an optional trailing decorative icon","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"inverse"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": like the "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" layout but with a trailing switch indicator and a leading optional decorative icon"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"anchor":"Indicator-states","text":"Indicator states","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The switch indicator has two available states set as a boolean property that determines whether the toggle is on or off."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Particular-cases","text":"Particular cases","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A dedicated look and feel is implemented for that if the ","type":"text"},{"code":"isError","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" flag is risen.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"In addition, the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" can be in read only mode, i.e. the user cannot interact with the component yet but this component must not be considered","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"as disabled.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The switch can be also outlined in some cases.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","text":"Accessibility considerations","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}]},{"type":"text","text":" will use several elements to describe the component: if component disabled \/ read only, if error context, the label and helper texts and a custom switch trait."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Forbidden-by-design","text":"Forbidden by design","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a read only component."}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component.","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both a read only and a disabled component."}],"type":"strong"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Code-samples","text":"Code samples","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected state","    @Published var isOn: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn)","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label, but in read only mode (user cannot interact yet, but not disabled).","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn, isReadOnly: true)","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label, and an helper text.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn, helper: \"The Beatles\")","","    \/\/ A leading switch with an additional label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn, additionalLabel: \"The Beatles\", helper: \"1967\")","","    \/\/ A trailing switch with a label, an additonal label, an helper text and an icon.","    \/\/ The inverse layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\",","                   isOn: $isOn,","                   additionalLabel: \"The Beatles\",","                   helper: \"1967\",","                   isReversed: true,","                   icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"))","","    \/\/ A trailing switch with a label, an helper text, an icon, a divider and is about an error.","    \/\/ The inverse layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Rescue from this world!\",","                   isOn: $isOn,","                   helper: \"Put your hand in mine\",","                   icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"),","                   isReversed: true,","                   isError: true,","                   hasDivider: true)","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label, but disabled.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Rescue from this world!\", isOn: $isOn)","        .disabled(true)","","    \/\/ Never disable a read only or an error-related switch as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Kaboom!\", isOn: $isOn, isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Kaboom!\", isOn: $isOn, isReadyOnly: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"],"syntax":"swift"},{"anchor":"Design-documentation","text":"Design documentation","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/18acc0-switch","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1.1.0 (Figma component design version)"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside","style":"note","name":"Version"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"0.14.0","type":"text"}]}],"type":"aside","style":"note","name":"Since"}],"kind":"content"}],"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem\/init(_:isOn:helper:icon:flipIcon:isReversed:isError:isReadOnly:hasDivider:)"],"anchor":"Initializers","title":"Initializers","generated":true},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem\/body"],"anchor":"Instance-Properties","title":"Instance Properties","generated":true},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentat